<Layout title="VashonMesh - Join Us">
  <main>
    <section class="content">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Welcome</h2>
        <p>
          We're not a formal group but if you want to help plan the network's future r have technical questions, we tend to gather:
          <ul>
            <li>on Vashon's Discord server (#vashon) 
              <li>or join the local radio club, <a href="https://w7vmi.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">W7VMI</a></li>
              <li>or join the club's email server at <a href="https://groups.io/g/W7VMI" target="_blank" rel="noopener">groups.io/g/V7VMI</a></li>
        </p>
        <p>
          Check our blog for upcoming events and workshops on mesh networking and related topics.
          </p>
        <p>
          Feel free to <a href="ContactUs" >contact us</a> if you have questions or want to get involved!
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  </Layout>